## Dotfile Management

These instructions are managed by chezmoi. The file you are reading is a rendered artifact — never edit it directly. Chezmoi will overwrite any direct changes on the next `apply`.

Source of truth: `~/.local/share/chezmoi/`

Shared rules live in `.chezmoitemplates/` and are composed into CLI-specific entry points in `dot_claude/` and `dot_gemini/`. To make changes, edit the source files there and run `chezmoi apply`.

Further environment details are in `ENVIRONMENT.md`.
